<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        color: #333333;
      }
      .container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px 0;
      }
      .button-container {
        text-align: center;
      }
      .button {
        background-color: #e74c3c;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 15px 25px;
        text-decoration: none;
        display: inline-block;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-radius: 5px;
      }

      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 20px;
        color: #999999;
      }
      .social-icons {
        margin-top: 20px;
        display: inline-block;
      }
      .social-icons img {
        width: 24px;
        margin: 0 10px;
      }
      .footer-text {
        margin-top: 10px;
        font-size: 12px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h2>Hello, {{username}}!</h2>
      </div>
      <p>Someone (hopefully you) has requested a password reset on your account. Please confirm that you requested this password reset by clicking on the link below. You will receive an email with your new password.</p>
      
      <div class="button-container">
      <a href="{{resetLink}}" class="button">RESET PASSWORD!</a>
    </div>

      <p>If you did not request this modification, just forget this email. Your password will remain the same.</p>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>purrfectCare Team</p>
        <div class="social-icons">
          <a href="#"><img src="facebook-icon.png" alt="Facebook"></a>
          <a href="#"><img src="instagram-icon.png" alt="Instagram"></a>
          <a href="#"><img src="twitter-icon.png" alt="Twitter"></a>
        </div>
        <p class="footer-text">
          2011 - 2021 Â© purrfectCare <br>
          <a href="www.purrfectCare.com">www.purrfectCare.com</a> <br>
          If you need help, please contact us at <a href="mailto:mdshohed170@gmail.com">mdshohed170@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
